{"tid":370594,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"返輪班 12點開工 但打緊十號波 老闆扣鐘犯唔犯法？","createTime":"2017-08-23T06:20:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-23T06:49:29.000Z","uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cdf4ace3fed714efe802d3828440e6a6a4fe5afa","tid":370594,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T06:20:59.000Z","msg":"返輪班 12點開工 <br />\n但打緊十號波 無車返<br />\n如果四點落到8號 我四點半先返到去<br />\n老闆要我第日補返四個半鐘會唔會犯法？"},{"pid":"3ae1cabfbf42ae28dbd000072cfb2d4502f4ff17","tid":370594,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T06:33:54.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"56433461ab9ef84c30d7249aaa28549f8ffc41dd","tid":370594,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T06:34:14.000Z","msg":"屌 已經8號 係時候動身開工"},{"pid":"d03741fdd651a867ef9fa563dca32cf54ef329f9","tid":370594,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T06:49:29.000Z","msg":"僱主不能以年假、法定假日及休息日補償損失之工作時間<br />\n<br />\n如僱主減少僱員有權享有的年假、法定假日及休息日，以補償因發出8號或以上颱風警告或黑色暴雨警告而損失的工作時間，即屬違法。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢唔用假黎扣 用鐘黎扣<br />\n如果全日因十號波返唔多<br />\n扣你十個鐘<br />\n咁其實咪一撚樣<br />\n奴工始終逃唔過俾人剝削既命運<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}